                            <comment id="317380" author="jamesanunez" created="Wed, 3 Nov 2021 18:01:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We haven&apos;t seen this test fail with this error message in over a year. We do still see the errors in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14325&quot; title=&quot;Interop: replay-single test 134 fails with &amp;#39;touch non-pfl file failed&amp;#39;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-14325&quot;&gt;LU-14325&lt;/a&gt; and a version check should be added to fix that issue. Thus, let&apos;s close this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
